              movies, preferred genres, and current mood to generate intelligent
              recommendations tailored specifically to you.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4">
            <h5>
              <i class="fas fa-database text-primary me-2"></i>Comprehensive
              Movie Data
            </h5>
            <p>
              We use the Open Movie Database (OMDb) API to provide detailed
              information about thousands of movies, including plot summaries,
              cast details, ratings, and more.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4">
            <h5>
              <i class="fas fa-user-circle text-primary me-2"></i>Personalized
              Experience
            </h5>
            <p>
              Unlike generic recommendation systems, MovieMind takes into
              account your specific preferences and even your current mood to
              suggest movies you're likely to enjoy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

